ier when you know someone&amp;rsquo;s got your back&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nivi:&lt;/strong&gt; Earlier, we talked about compound interest, but we didn&amp;rsquo;t dig into it much.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
